      "content": "it just feels like i'm a ghost haunting my own house. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it's like i'm just a shell. everything i do... making breakfast, going to work, even breathing... it's all just unnecessary effort. it feels like i'm just dragging this body around for no reason. if he's gone, then the part of me that actually lived is gone too. why am i even still here?",
